messages:
Name: Ismail Köybasi
Nationality: Turkey
Date of Birth: July 10, 1989
Position: Defender
Current club: Rizespor
Süper Lig clubs played for: Gaziantepspor, Beşiktaş, Fenerbahçe, Rizespor

Ismail Köybasi is a Rizespor defender who has played in the majority of their Süper Lig games in 2020/2021, making 20 appearances overall and accumulating 1,245 minutes of playing time. He has started in 14 of these appearances across their 40 fixtures and been used as a substitute on six occasions.

Köybasi last played in the competition on May 11 for Rizespor against Gaziantep FK. He netted a goal and assisted another in that game for his team in their 5-4 win. In total, the defender has scored three Süper Lig goals this term, and provided two assists. He has been booked three times.
A first goal of the league campaign for Köybasi came against Antalyaspor in a 3-2 victory on April 16.
In last season's Primera División, Köybasi featured in four games for Granada.
Köybasi switched to Rizespor in October 2020 from Granada, for whom he made four league appearances in total.
